<h3>Smeargle</h3>
<ul>
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6-sss9giRHo">Video guide</a>
  <li>Catch Smeargle and breed until it has 31 Speed IV and +Speed nature (ex: Jolly, Timid)
    <ul>
      <li>Catch a Female Smeargle or Ditto with the correct nature, and give it an Everstone when breeding.</li>
      <li>Have a Pokémon with ability Magma Armour or Flame Body in the first slot to hatch eggs faster.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Get a Gyarados with Dragon Rage (Level 25). Battle Ditto. Use Dragon Rage. Ditto uses Dragon Rage. Put Ditto to Sleep. Switch to Smeargle. Sketch Dragon Rage.</li>
  <li>Give Smeargle x10 Carbos</li>
  <li>Give Smeargle Pokérus (not needed, but without it, resulting Smeargle will only have 17 Speed)</li>
  <li>Give Smeargle a Macro Brace. Get x5 other Pokémon with Exp. Share (not needed, but without it, resulting Smeargle will only have 17 Speed).</li>
  <li>In Route 103, battle level 2 Wingull. During the battle, switch to all other 5 Pokémon. This ensures Smearlge earns only 1 exp per battle.</li>
  <li>Repeat until Smeargle is about to raise to level 6.</li>
  <li>Level 5 Smeargle should have 18 Speed.</li>
  <li>Repeat all the same steps to have x2 Level 5 Smeargle with 18 Speed and Dragon Rage.</li>
</ul>

